snippet.title: Amber Heard Misses Court Deposition And Appears Unfazed
snippet.description:
Friday, August 12, 2016 - Amber Heard arrives in Los Angeles on a flight in from London several hours after her scheduled deposition in her case against Johnny Depp Friday morning. After her lawyers quickly worked to get a 24-reprieve from the judge in her favor, the deposition was rescheduled for Saturday. Amber looks unfazed passing through the airport, even somewhat nonchalant about the proceedings ahead of her.
